{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/font-family-name-quotes/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-case/","description":"color-hex-length 指定 16 进制颜色的简写或扩写。 命令行中的 --fix 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的所有问题。 选项 string: \"short\"|\"long\" \"short\" 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规： \"long\"…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"color-hex-length\"><a href=\"#color-hex-length\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>color-hex-length</h1>\n<p>指定 16 进制颜色的简写或扩写。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span> }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**        ↑\n * 这个 16 进制颜色 */</span></code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"../../../../user-guide/cli/#%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF\">命令行</a>中的 <code>--fix</code> 选项可以自动修复此规则报告的所有问题。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"short\"|\"long\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"short\"><a href=\"#short\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"short\"</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ffffff</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ffffffaa</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fffa</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#a4a4a4</span>; }</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"long\"><a href=\"#long\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"long\"</code></h3>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fffa</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ffffff</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#ffffffaa</span>; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/color-hex-length.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-length/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-length/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-length/index.html.325164ba712ea37055974593341d28e8.json"}